==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Audacity
<hw>Au*dac"i*ty</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn>
<def>Daring spirit, resolution, or confidence;
venturesomeness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>The freedom and <qex>audacity</qex> necessary in the commerce of
men.</q> <rj><qau>Tatler.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Reckless daring; presumptuous impudence; -- implying
a contempt of law or moral restraints.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>With the most arrogant <qex>audacity</qex>.</q>
<rj><qau>Joye.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>audad</ent>⟦br⟧
